The pipe squeeze is an Agility shortcut found in the Brimhaven Dungeon. The shortcut connects the Black demon area of the dungeon with the Red dragon area. 34 Agility is required to get from the red dragons to black demons, but the shortcut has no requirements when going the opposite direction. This shortcut does not appear on the minimap or the World map.

The '''pipe squeeze''' is an [[Agility]] [[shortcut]] found in the [[Brimhaven Dungeon]]. The shortcut connects the [[Black demon]] area of the dungeon with the [[Red dragon]] area. 34 Agility is required to get from the red dragons to black demons, but the shortcut has no requirements when going the opposite direction. This shortcut does not appear on the minimap or the World map.
